graph TD
    A[Start Consumer Poll Loop] --> B[poll Duration]
    B --> C{Records Returned?}
    C -- No --> B
    C -- Yes --> D[Process Records Batch]
    
    subgraph Processing Block
        D --> E[Loop: For Record in Records]
        E --> F[Deserialize & Parse JSON]
        F -- Success --> G[Execute Business Logic]
        F -- Failure/Poison Pill --> H[Route to DLQ / Log & Skip]
        G --> I[Store Offset + 1 in currentOffsets Map]
        H --> I
        I --> E
    end
    
    E -- All Records Processed --> J{enable.auto.commit = false?}
    J -- Yes --> K[commitSync currentOffsets]
    J -- No --> L[Background Auto-Commit Thread Handles It]
    
    K --> M[Clear currentOffsets Map]
    M --> B
    L --> B
